[SN]TITLE[SN]
Boy, 15, charged over Torryburn Hotel in Kintore fire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A teenager has been charged after a "major blaze" at a derelict hotel in Aberdeenshire.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The fire was discovered at the Torryburn Hotel in Kintore at about 23:30 on Monday.
About 40 firefighters attended the incident.
Police Scotland said that a 15-year-old boy had been charged in connection with the fire.
